   <section remap="concept" id="toolsconcept">
      <title id="ttld95e9" remap="title">Tools</title>
      <para id="parad95e12" remap="shortdesc">Invest in a good set of tools for doing all kinds of tasks around the house.</para>
      <para id="parad95e16" remap="p">Useful tools include the following items:</para>
